$\\beta^-$ detection efficiencies was found to be\nin the range $10^{-44}$ to $10^{-36}$ cm$^{2}$. For experiments that uses the\nend point to determine the neutrino mass, interference due to mixing should be\ntaken into account.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Apr 2022 18:49:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-26"}
