2})$ plane and are even in $y_{2}$ for the Schr\\\"{o}dinger-Newton\nsystem by the Lyapunov-Schmidt reduction method. We extend the results got by\nDuan et al. in (arXiv:2006.16125v1) to the nonlinear Schr\\\"{o}dinger-Newton\nsystem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Apr 2022 03:05:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-26"}
