e-of-the-art HTAP systems, with average\ntransactional/analytical throughput improvements of 1.7x/3.7x, and reduces\nenergy consumption by 48% over the prior lowest-energy HTAP system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 24 Apr 2022 13:40:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-26"}
